{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block body %}

<div class="card">
	<div class="card-header">
        <h5 class="card-title mb-0">
            {{ "Terms and Conditions" }}
        </h5>
	</div>
	<div class="card-body h-100">
        <h2>
            {{ "1. Acceptance of Terms" }}
        </h2>
        <p>
            {{ 
                "
                By accessing and using our website, you agree to these terms and conditions. If you do not agree, please refrain from using our services.
                "
            }}
        </p>

        <h2>
            {{ "2. Services Provided" }}
        </h2>
        <p>
            {{ 
                "
                Our website offers [describe the services provided, e.g., a sales platform, booking service, etc.]. We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any service at any time without notice.
                "
            }}
        </p>

        <h2>
            {{ "3. Registration and User Account" }}
        </h2>
        <p>
            {{ 
                "
                Users must provide accurate information when creating an account.
                You are responsible for keeping your login details confidential.
                Any activity conducted through your account is your responsibility.
                "
            }}
        </p>

        <h2>
            {{ "4. Personal Data Protection" }}
        </h2>
        <p>
            {{ 
                "
                We collect and process your personal data in accordance with our [Privacy Policy]. Your information is securely encrypted to protect your privacy.
                "
            }}
        </p>

        <h2>
            {{ "5. Intellectual Property" }}
        </h2>
        <p>
            {{ 
                "
                All content on this site (texts, images, videos, logos) is protected by copyright and other intellectual property laws. Unauthorized reproduction is prohibited.
                "
            }}
        </p>

        <h2>
            {{ "6. User Responsibilities" }}
        </h2>
        <p>
            {{ 
                "
                Users agree not to:

                Use the site for illegal purposes;
                Violate the rights of other users;
                Attempt to disrupt the functioning of the site.
                "
            }}
        </p>

        <h2>
            {{ "7. Limitation of Liability" }}
        </h2>
        <p>
            {{ 
                "
                We disclaim any liability for any direct or indirect damages resulting from the use of or inability to access our website.
                "
            }}
        </p>

        <h2>
            {{ "8. Changes to Terms" }}
